  },
  {
    "content_id": 695534,
    "reference_id": 121692,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "2 Timothée 1.2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "55001002",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p><strong>Quelle est la relation que Paul entretient avec Timothée ?</strong></p><p>Paul entretient une relation étroite avec Timothée, puisqu&apos;il l&apos;appelle son « enfant bien-aimé ».</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "55001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:2",
          "end_ref": "55001002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 695535,
    "reference_id": 121693,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "2 Timothée 1.4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "55001004",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p><span><strong>Alors que Paul se souvient de Timothée dans ses prières, que est le désir de son coeur ?</strong></span></p><p>Le désir du coeur de Paul est de voir Timothée.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "55001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:4",
          "end_ref": "55001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 695536,
    "reference_id": 121694,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "2 Timothée 1.5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "55001005",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p><span><strong>Dans la famille de Timothée, qui possédait déjà une foi authentique ?</strong></span></p><p><span>Sa grand-mère et sa mère manifestaient toutes deux une foi authentique.</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "55001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:5",
          "end_ref": "55001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 695537,
    "reference_id": 121695,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "2 Timothée 1.7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "55001007",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p><span><strong>Quel genre d&apos;esprit Dieu a-t-il donné à Timothée ?</strong></span></p><p><span>Dieu a donné à Timothée un esprit caractérisé par la force, l&apos;amour et la sagesse.</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "55001007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:7",
          "end_ref": "55001007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 695538,
    "reference_id": 121696,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "2 Timothée 1.8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "55001008",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p><span><strong>Qu&apos;est-ce que Paul demande à Timothée d&apos;éviter ?</strong></span></p><p><span>Paul lui demande de ne pas avoir honte de témoigner du Seigneur.</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "55001008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:8",
          "end_ref": "55001008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 695539,
    "reference_id": 121697,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "2 Timothée 1.8 (#2)",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "55001008",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p><strong>Qu&apos;est-ce que Paul demande à Timothée de faire ?</strong></p><p><span>Paul demande à Timothée de souffrir avec lui pour l&apos;Évangile.</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "55001008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:8",
          "end_ref": "55001008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 695540,
    "reference_id": 121698,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "2 Timothée 1.9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "55001009",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p><strong>Q</strong><span><strong>uand Dieu nous a-t-il accordé de bénéficier de son plan et de sa grâce ?</strong></span></p><p><span>Le plan de Dieu et sa grâce nous ont été donnés avant les temps éternels.</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "55001009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:9",
          "end_ref": "55001009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 695541,
    "reference_id": 121699,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "2 Timothée 1.10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "55001010",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p><strong>De quelle manière Dieu a-t-il révélé son plan de salut ?</strong></p><p>Dieu a révélé son plan de salut par l&apos;apparition de notre Sauveur, Jésus-Christ.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "55001010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:10",
          "end_ref": "55001010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 695542,
    "reference_id": 121700,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "2 Timothée 1.10 (#2)",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "55001010",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p><strong>Lorsqu&apos;il est apparu, que fit Jésus concernant la mort, la vie et l&apos;immortalité ?</strong></p><p>Jésus mit fin à la mort et révéla la vie et l&apos;immortalité par l&apos;Évangile.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "55001010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:10",
          "end_ref": "55001010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 695543,
    "reference_id": 121701,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "2 Timothée 1.12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "55001012",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p><strong>Pourquoi Paul est-il sûr que Dieu peut agir en sa faveur, pour qu&apos;il n&apos;ait aucune honte d&apos;annoncer l&apos;Évangile ?</strong></p><p>Paul est persuadé que Dieu <span>a la puissance de garder son dépôt jusqu’à la fin.</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "55001012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:12",
          "end_ref": "55001012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 695544,
    "reference_id": 121702,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "2 Timothée 1.14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "55001014",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p><strong>Comment Timothée peut-il garder le précieux dépôt que Dieu lui a confié ?</strong></p><p>Timothée doit conserver le précieux dépôt que Dieu lui a confié en s&apos;appuyant sur le Saint-Esprit.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "55001014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:14",
          "end_ref": "55001014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "2TI 1:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 695545,
    "reference_id": 121703,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "2 Timothée 1.15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "55001015",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p><strong>Comment les compagnons d’Asie de Paul se sont-ils comportés envers lui ?</strong></p><p>Ils se sont tous détournés de lui.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "55001015",
